sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as 用户
    participant Session as QueryPanel / Session
    participant FrontAPI as shared/api.ts
    participant API as FastAPI /api/query
    participant Coord as MultiAgentCoordinator
    participant Flow as workflow
    participant City as CityResolver
    participant Weather as WeatherService
    participant Knowledge as FashionKnowledge
    participant Fashion as FashionAgent
    participant Present as Presentation
    participant UI as Session / UI

    User->>Session: 提交文本地点或地图点位
    Session->>Session: 组装 QueryRequest\nquery_text / selected_coords / confirmation_mode / locale
    Session->>FrontAPI: postQuery(payload)
    FrontAPI->>API: POST /api/query
    API->>API: 生成 request_id\n记录 query.started 事件
    API->>Coord: process_query(payload)
    Coord->>Flow: run_query_workflow(QueryState)

    alt 复杂查询且 LLM 可用
        Flow->>Coord: 调用 planner 节点
        Coord->>Coord: 生成 QueryPlan（LLM planner）
    else 普通查询或已有选中候选/坐标
        Flow->>Coord: 走 fast path
        Coord->>Coord: 生成默认 QueryPlan
    end

    Flow->>City: resolve_city(...)
    City-->>Flow: CityResolutionResult

    alt strict 模式或需要澄清候选
        Flow-->>Coord: 返回 needs_clarification
        Coord->>Present: build_result_view_model(clarification result)
        Present-->>API: QueryResponse(view_model)
        API-->>FrontAPI: 200 OK
        FrontAPI-->>UI: 返回候选地点确认 view_model
        UI->>UI: 展示 CandidateConfirmCard / 提示消息
    else 地点已确认
        Flow->>Weather: fetch weather by city / coords

        alt OpenWeather 已配置
            Weather-->>Flow: WeatherResult(live / forecast)
        else OpenWeather 未配置
            Weather-->>Flow: WeatherResult(demo / degraded)
        end

        Flow->>Fashion: get_fashion_advice(weather, locale, query_context)
        Fashion->>Knowledge: retrieve_knowledge_hits(weather, context, locale)
        Knowledge-->>Fashion: KnowledgeHit[]

        alt LLM 可用
            Fashion-->>Flow: FashionAdviceResult(LLM + 规则融合)
        else LLM 不可用
            Fashion-->>Flow: FashionAdviceResult(规则兜底)
        end

        Flow-->>Coord: CoordinatorResult
        Coord->>Present: build_result_view_model(result)
        Present-->>API: QueryResponse(view_model)
        API-->>FrontAPI: 200 OK
        FrontAPI-->>UI: 返回 view_model
        UI->>UI: 更新结果区、进度条、notice
        UI->>UI: 更新历史/收藏状态与最近查询
    end

    par 后端观测链
        API->>API: 写 step trace / app.events.jsonl / logs
    and 前端本地状态链
        UI->>UI: 写 sessionStorage / localStorage
    end
